    "This focus on brain cancer is likely due to the change in classification standards of gliomas in 2016, in which the World Health Organization added molecular features as decision standards to histopathological ones [104].",
    "Thus, studies that would have solely relied on histopathology in the past, would now also require genomic evidence.",
